en_474420_0	A felicitation ceremony was held at the Presidential Secretariat President Maithripala Sirisena to recognize artistes who won international awards.
en_474420_1	President Maithripala Sirisena handed over cash awards to the artistes who won awards at the International Film and Television Awards ceremonies this year.
en_474420_2	The artistes who bagged awards at the Niece Awards in France, the Osaka Asian Film Festival in Japan and the Moscow International Film and Television Awards.
en_474420_3	Accordingly, Nita Fernando ,NilminiSigera,Kumara Karavdeniya,ShiranRatnayake,Ranga Bandaranaike ,AthulaPeiris and Nishadi Bandaranaike received their cash awards from the President.
en_474420_4	Meanwhile, the President also made a donation for the alumni of the University of Peradeniya.
en_474420_5	The President also donated money to the sportsmen and women who are leaving for the World Gymnastic Festival and the Sri Lanka Police Cricket Team attending the International Police Cricket Festival.
